invalid type: string "WHO Infant Feeding and Breastfeeding Guidelines:\n1. Exclusive Breastfeeding:\nWHO recommends that infants should be exclusively breastfed for the first six months of life to achieve\noptimal growth, development, and health. No water, formula, or other foods should be given unless\nmedically indicated.\n2. Initiation of Breastfeeding:\nd Trimester Milestones (Weeks 28 to 40):